Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.57,0:43:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably there's all kinds of work to do on the other side, too.\NIf there's a lot of work on this side I suppose there's a lot of work on the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.57,0:43:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you think?\NI imagine there's a lot of work to do.
